<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">

<head>
    <meta charset="utf-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>이상형 월드컵 시작</title>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
    <script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.3/dist/js/bootstrap.bundle.min.js"></script>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="/css/style.css">
</head>

<body>
{{> layout/navbar}}
<div class="common-middle-box text-center">
    <h1>{{worldcup.title}}</h1>
    <h3>{{#worldcup.description}}{{worldcup.description}}{{/worldcup.description}}</h3>

    <div class="d-flex justify-content-center">
        <img src="/img/test.png" style="width: 250px; height: 250px;">
    </div>
    <p class="text-muted text-center">
        <small>라운드를 선택해 주세요</small>
    </p>
    <form action="/worldcups/start-form/{{id}}" method="POST">
        <select id="mySelect" name="round" class="form-select" aria-label="Default select example">
            {{#round}}
                <option value="{{.}}">{{.}}강</option>
            {{/round}}
        </select>
        <p class="text-muted text-center fs-6">
            총{{allItem}}명의 후보중 무작위 <span id="round">{{fight}}</span>명이 대결합니다
        </p>
        <button type="submit" class="btn block w-100 mb-2 common-color-primary common-none-ouline-button text-white">
            게임 시작
        </button>
    </form>
</div>
</body>
<script>
    // 콤보박스 이벤트
    document.querySelector("#mySelect").addEventListener("change",() => {
        // 선택된 option 요소 가져오기
        var selectedOption = document.querySelector("#mySelect option:checked");
        var selectedValue = selectedOption.value;
        document.querySelector("#round").textContent = selectedValue;
    });

</script>
</html>